Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我的幻覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帕拉斯的城樓頂擁抱著的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚我見到了我從未見過的亞連的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與那傢伙一起飛離了帕拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號碼輸入完畢後請按下＃字鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將話筒掛上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野…學長?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我捨棄了一切前來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄了一切?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是國家 戰爭還是騎士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都只為了見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你等很久了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞…亞連?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使飛舞之日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,我竟然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續睡沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在喊著"亞連,救救我"說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒死心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也還真悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,你還差點就被賣給梅甸了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是亞連趕過來,我們就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實生的比較好吃說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,這樣也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得其它的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的唇膏跟我的手錶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得這個味道怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我下來,你這隻貓小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了,你這只笨貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得它們蠻像的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會有那顆石頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我小時候收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,現在變成了我奶奶的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有其他家人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,爸爸跟媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王 母后是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我老是跟我弟吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是愛頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後挨罵的卻總是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"小瞳,你是姊姊啊"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"小瞳,你都已經是高中生了"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"小瞳你是個女孩子耶"之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸卻老是笑笑地在一旁聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得他們現在過得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父王與母后在我小時候就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在法尼利亞變成一片焦土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾卡斯也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稱的上是我家人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只剩她一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫他王兄嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…弗肯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前,他因為害怕參加王位繼承儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕與龍對戰而開溜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他竟然會去投靠寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,那傢伙居然還想殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,我太激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下來有什麼打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過這次的事件,我瞭解到自己還太過天真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續鍛煉劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切從這裏重新開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能回到亞連的國家去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我現在是寨巴哈軍的追捕對像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我一起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,況且說不定還有機會要借助你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你能回到那邊去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備要攻打他國了,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王,請將理由告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為何要將亞連關進大牢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個毛頭小子不知道會搞出什麼花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要他暫時先安分點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連有做了什麼壞事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不光是協助艾斯嘉科尼逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還打算與寨巴哈為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王您才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會允許那些艦隊駐紮我國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣與其說是同盟國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是照著寨巴哈的命令在行事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是情非得已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是瑪蓮妮…那孩子還活著的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪蓮妮王姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道寨巴哈打算去攻打弗雷特公國嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然身為公主那你就該多為國家未來考量才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情竟然會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞德羅福斯將軍下令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石數量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速採掘及運送作業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都不為現場的人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只是一頭龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是龍的墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的占卜根本就不准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我們帶來這種危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是佔卜安全的方位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的占卜說不定是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不能到這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我已經得到父王的同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並未聽說過有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻煩你幫我看看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迦迪斯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的墳場是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍在臨死前會來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他們又在挖什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要從龍的化石中採集出能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六架人型裝甲是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那採到能源石之後要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來作為人型裝甲的動力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你說的能源石是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼的能源也是來自於能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確來說應該是"龍能源石"才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型裝甲還有浮遊船的動力都是來自於龍能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要像這樣從龍的墳場挖出能源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰場上也是擁有較多龍能源石的人獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人在這裏躲好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓寨巴哈稱心如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷特?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈要攻打弗雷特公國?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王他打算對西特王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他自己的外孫見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能夠阻止這件事的,只有你而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論到哪裏,我都會陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大還沒來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也差不多要察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長,我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜,我會幫你瞞著父王的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起回城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心了,王姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟亞連一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要離開這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主,請保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們,準備起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的,手要動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人型裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守備隊快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石的倉庫?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要毀了那裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度在追捕的艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個無情的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:16:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是多倫卡喀大人要找的龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是怎麼找到這裏的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這男孩真不聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來為這位小姐介紹個朋友認識好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被它咬上一□包你馬上沒命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很聽從我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜,過去打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜,送個友誼之吻給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真心誠意的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人的信號嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,別再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的士兵在,快去躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要毀了那座倉庫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他往倉庫去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石產生反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在產生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你在哪裏?天野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶祝會要開始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:22:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接把你給毀了如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命中注定的相會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:56.85,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:05.30,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:12.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:19.08,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.44,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:26.45,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:34.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:38.10,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:41.60,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:49.07,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:56.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:05.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:12.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:19.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:21.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:26.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:34.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:38.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:41.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:49.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

